$PROBLEM THEOPHYLLINE ORAL P:ROOT F:BASE $INPUT ID AMT TIME DV BWT $DATA THEOPP $SUBROUTINE ADVAN2 TRANS2 $PK TVCL = THETA(1) TVV = THETA(2) TVKA = THETA(3) CL = TVCL * EXP(ETA(1)) V = TVV * EXP(ETA(2)) KA = TVKA * EXP(ETA(3)) S2 = V K = CL / V
$ERROR IPRED = F W = SQRT(THETA(4)**2 + THETA(5)**2 * IPRED**2) IRES = DV - IPRED IWRES = IRES / W Y = IPRED + W * EPS(1)
$THETA (0,0.1) (0,1) (0,10) 0.1 FIX (0,0.5) $OMEGA BLOCK(3) 0.2 0.1 0.2 0.1 0.1 0.2 $SIGMA 1 FIX $ESTIMATION METHOD=COND INTERACTION NOABORT PRINT=5 MAXEVALS=0 $TABLE ID MDV DV ONEHEADER NOPRINT NOAPPEND FILE=npctab.dta
